Easily Create Decision Tables by using Templates

You are here:
SALESFORCE HELP
DOCS
Salesforce Summer ’24 Release Notes

Save time and effort in creating a decision table by using industry-specific templates. Use these templates to quickly create a decision table based on your business requirement, instead of creating it from scratch. The templates are available in your Salesforce org only if your Industries solution has shipped it.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions for Industries clouds where Business Rules Engine is enabled.
title: Easily Create Decision Tables by using Templates
